The date of this synod is not recorded, but from the closing words of the chapter it may be inferred to have been held a considera- ble time before the writing of these memoirs; possibly before Adamnan became abbot, or at least at an early period of his incumbency. The recorded visits of Adamnan to Ireland are at 687 (Ul. 636), 689, 692 (Ul. 691), 697 (171. 696), of Tighernach.
